title: Chloe Cane Cuckold
description: Chloe's better half Kade doesn't believe her for reasons unknown. He has a sneaking suspicion that she might be sneaking around on him. Rather than standing up to her with his fears like a genuine man, he chose to go on a chase for her journal. All things considered, what says "I adore you" more than the contemptible befouling of your better half's most individual and private of possessions? Try not to stress over Chloe, however; karma has a method for sorting this sort of crap out in a rush!
